resources.name: Post Session
resources.description:
Login de Usuario. Não precisa de autenticação.

Request:

<!--RESPONse-->
	{
		"email": "doug@mail.com",
		"password": "123456"
	}
<!--ENDRESPONse-->

Response: Status 200.

<!--RESPONse-->
	{
		"token": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJlbWFpbCI6Im5leHRhZ2VAbWFpbC5jb20iLCJpc0FjdGl2ZSI6dHJ1ZSwiaWF0IjoxNjc5NDk5MzE4LCJleHAiOjE2Nzk1ODU3MTgsInN1YiI6IjY1Nzg2NzRhLWRmZDUtNGRiNy1hNzg5LTAxM2ZlN2RmYWJhYiJ9.oUKJhJabEawwkJkp0It9SHai-sKrUQoFms7REBQvp2s"
	}
<!--ENDRESPONse-->

<!--RESPONse-->
	{
		"message": "Email or password invalid!"

resources.name: Post User
resources.description:
Criação de um novo usuario. Não precisa de autenticação.

Request:
<!--RESPONse-->
	{
		"name": "Henrique",
		"email": "henrique@mail.com",
		"password": "123456",
		"photo": "https://www.petz.com.br/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/enxoval-para-gato-Copia.jpg",
		"phone": "11 99999 9999"
	}
<!--ENDRESPONse-->

Response: Status 201.

<!--RESPONse-->
	{
		"id": "b82c0d0e-2ac4-4b43-a406-a5e84e883441",
		"name": "Henrique",
		"email": "henrique1@mail.com",
		"photo": null,
		"phone": "12 99999 9999",
		"isActive": true,
		"createdAt": "2023-03-27T14:54:22.371Z",
		"updatedAt": "2023-03-27T14:54:22.371Z"
	}
<!--ENDRESPONse-->

É possivel cadastra usuario sem o campo de photo. 

Request:
<!--RESPONse-->
	{
		"name": "Henrique",
		"email": "henrique4@mail.com",
		"password": "123456",
		"phone": "15 99999 9999"
	}
<!--ENDRESPONse-->

Response: Status 201

<!--RESPONse-->
	{
		"updatedAt": "2023-03-23T15:48:17.220Z",
		"createdAt": "2023-03-23T15:48:17.220Z",
		"isActive": true,
		"phone": "15 99999 9999",
		"photo": null,
		"email": "henrique4@mail.com",
		"name": "Henrique",
		"id": "83186a4d-ea5c-43bf-b697-c90278bcfcda"
	}
<!--ENDRESPONse-->

Erro quando você não passa os campos obrigatorios.

Response: Status 400.

<!--RESPONse-->
	{
		"message": [
			"name is a required field",
			"email is a required field",
			"password is a required field",
			"phone is a required field"
		]
	}
<!--ENDRESPONse-->

Erro de cadastrar um usuario existe.

Response: Status 409.

<!--RESPONse-->
	{
		"message": "User exists!"
	}
<!--ENDRESPONse-->

resources.name: Get user ID

	{
		"id": "dd081cef-d149-4732-b405-4b40d4b614f5",

		"photo": null,
		"phone": "11 99999 9999",
		"isActive": true,
		"createdAt": "2023-03-27T14:40:34.859Z",
		"updatedAt": "2023-03-27T14:40:34.859Z"
	}
<!--ENDRESPONse-->

Erro quando a rota não esta autenticada.

Response: Status 401.

		"message": "jwt must be provided"
	}

		"message": "User does not exist!"
	}

<!--RESPONse-->
	{
		"message": "Internal server error"
	}
